snippet.title: Sneak Out Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Sneak Out is a crazy hide & seek game in a huge magical castle with up to 5 hiders playing against one dangerous seeker. Maybe you will be sneaky enough to complete all the tasks and get out of the mysterious castle or enough determined to hunt everyone else down.
 
Come and visit us on https://sneak-out.kinguin.net/ :)
